_header: One feler then three and fewer than five
_description: Tag translating Latin, ‘vno plures tribus & pauciores quinque…’ which follows it, in a series of Latin sentences with English translations in a schoolbook — written as prose

OxfLinLat129.Transcription:
On feler þen thre & fewer þan fyvyy hadde vp on my
                    c[r]ule strokes ful ryveOn feler þen thre & feler þan
                    fyvey plokkyd appullys ful ryve
